pages.text:
Elevated
Waterfront
As the sun sets over the horizon, witness a breathtaking display of colors that transforms the sky into a canvas of warmth. The twinkling lights reflecting on the water create an enchanting atmosphere, making every moment at our elevated waterfront restaurant truly magical.
Champagne
Sunsets
All Champagne Glass and Bottles - Half Price from 4-6 PM
Picture the sun dipping below the horizon, casting a warm, golden glow across the serene expanse of the waterfront. As hues of pink, orange, and purple paint the sky, guests at the Bayside Grille are treated to a mesmerizing spectacle that unfolds with each passing moment.
Keyribbean
Cooking
At the Bayside Grille, we invite you to embark on a culinary adventure that seamlessly combines the vibrant tastes of the Florida Keys with the rich and exotic flavors of the Caribbean. Our Keyribbean menu is a celebration of the best of both worlds, promising a symphony of tastes that dance on your palate.
Signature
Cocktails
Our in-house mixologists have artfully crafted a collection of signature cocktails that go beyond the ordinary, offering a sensorial journey that mirrors the culinary excellence of our menu. Each sip is a masterpiece, an orchestra of flavors that dance on your palate, creating an unforgettable experience.
Lunch
Indulge in the extraordinary with our Keyribbean Fusion Lunch Specials, a delightful blend of local flavors from the Florida Keys and the exotic tastes of the Caribbean.
From inventive starters to mouthwatering mains and decadent desserts, each dish is a masterpiece designed to captivate the senses.
Dinner
Prepare to be amazed by our innovative dinner menu, expertly curated by our passionate chefs. Each dish is a masterpiece, a blend of creativity and culinary expertise that pushes the boundaries of flavor. Discover the secrets behind our unique dinner experience that has captivated the taste buds and hearts of our patrons.
Sunday
Brunch
Join us at the Bayside Grile and make your Sundays extraordinary with a brunch experience that transcends the ordinary. From the first sip to the last bite, indulge in the luxury of an amazing Sunday brunch that leaves a lasting impression.
Come, savor the exceptional, and create delightful memories. Your extraordinary Sunday brunch awaits!
Boat
Dockage
Roll up to the Bayside Grille in style and make a splash with a dining experience that starts at the water's edge. Arrive effortlessly to our dock, and immerse yourself in the unparalleled combination of culinary excellence and waterfront ambiance.
Come, set sail for an unforgettable dining adventure at the Bayside Grille. Your table and a taste of the waterfront await!
